I think Kalius is a good second Magi becaus she has a power that works almost like a Warriors Boots but with a drawback of discarding the creature.<br>
<br>
Delia the vellup lady alright by know you might have more than 1 vellup in your hand but you can still use her effectively by playing the vellups and grabbing elder vellups from the deck, other than that its pretty basic.<br>
